cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper deals with the task of describing visual content, which is a common theme in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of crowdsourcing to gather image labels suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and human computation (cs.MM). Finally, the mention of attribute-based image search suggests a potential connection to information retrieval (cs.IR).
